<bibRefCitation author="Don, D." box="[607,797,568,595]" pageId="6" pageNumber="67" pagination="276 - 329" refId="ref24307" refString="Don, D. (1823) An illustration of the natural family of plants called Melastomaceae. Memoirs of the Wernerian Natural History Society 4 (2): 276 - 329." type="journal article" year="1823">Don (1823: 309)</bibRefCitation>
